list.name: Default
list.comment: Fix calculations to consistently use degrees C rather than degrees K. Previously we used degrees K, then switched to degrees C but failed to update the codebase throughout. Added more tets.

task.summary: Added IDE setup files, updated gitignore to ignore the CMake output files that are automatically produced by CLion.
Changed to read and support temperature in data sentences. Now switches to white circle as airball when the IAS is too small to reasonably display.
Improve probe math to match what was written in 2016 paper.
The main deployment binary, ab_device, was erroneously configured to use fake data. Fixed.
Adds gradually fading TAS ring to the display.
Modify airdata_plot binary to take a set of data sentences from stdin and augment them with computed values from our airdata model.
Fix calculations to consistently use degrees C rather than degrees K. Previously we used degrees K, then switched to degrees C but failed to update the codebase throughout. Added more tets.
